comments:
Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Healey with 
    Sutton. See also Table 2, note (f).

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parishes of Healey with Sutton, Masham 
    Moor, Ellingstring and Fearby. See also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Healey and 
    Ilton cum Pott. See also Table 2, notes (b), (c), (e) and (f).

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed parts of the parishes of 
    Fearby, Healey with Sutton and Masham Moor. See also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Healey, 
    Colsterdale and Ilton cum Pott. See also Table 2, note (f).

That part which until 1.4.1934 formed part of the parish of Arrathorne. See 
    also Table 2, note (e).
